{"tid":1753571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲熱血少年棄打機拉票","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:59:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07d2d250cb6406a65b3f0a984c349ddefadb9112","tid":1753571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/NU54HT3VB77MEGKACNARIDZBTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FNU54HT3VB77MEGKACNARIDZBTQ%2F&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM2929Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=0e199d89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FNU54HT3VB77MEGKACNARIDZBTQ%2F&h=2abc5dcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/NU54HT3VB77MEGKACNARIDZBTQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n14歲熱血少年棄打機拉票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191125/large/1574614373_675a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191125%2Flarge%2F1574614373_675a.gif&h=5e8535b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何小朋友（左）及阿偉為劉家衡拉票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【深水埗南昌北】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗南昌北選區氣氛熱鬧，有小朋友向排隊隊伍拉票。14歲的何小朋友是YouTuber，經營有關政治的頻道，昨早他在深水埗為公民黨劉家衡拉票，希望有票的大人可為他投票，「點解我哋唔可以喺屋企打機，我哋冇呢一票，你哋可唔可以幫我投呢一票畀劉家衡？」<br />\n<br />\n15歲的阿偉也有份助選，自6月9日起常到示威現場，批評政府6月12日堅持二讀，又以警方施放催淚彈鎮壓，無視200萬人大遊行，「我哋叫撤回佢就叫暫緩，7.21何君堯同白衣人握手，警察解釋遲咗39分鐘，見到啲人俾人打到頭破血流好心痛。」他望市民可代他投民主派議員，「鄭泳舜四年選完好似都冇再落區，最近又恐嚇毛漢，令我哋好憤怒」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王春怡"},{"pid":"b031e2fee28a1facaec47d93794359556a43304e","tid":1753571,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"jer霸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4f26a43414aec6284135131afd6c1ad8529866","tid":1753571,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"嘩屌好撚有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5dae477de2150f2f5df7c363332b122c4616c4","tid":1753571,"uid":2890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:28:32.000Z","msg":"4年後就係你地投票既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5151479bbbebf70761d9c5600b7a175e19f6d7f7","tid":1753571,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kQyBktm.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"706c3e2cfcd3f5ffd63972a79c55dd690a074e90","tid":1753571,"uid":338743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b15347a9b3f1d68b57d1390fed15f4b11cfd3a13","tid":1753571,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5c7e4fc91b6d5fbf1c5fe0ffd505fc0e529d04","tid":1753571,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"狙擊陳怡嗰個？"},{"pid":"7832e5d0a682432c595036e3277db7effd19a0cf","tid":1753571,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5c7e4fc91b6d5fbf1c5fe0ffd505fc0e529d04","tid":1753571,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"狙擊陳怡嗰個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"好似係"},{"pid":"8ca5abfc8f329e8f86413f0ea339b543cf92692d","tid":1753571,"uid":267680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"好感動"},{"pid":"954e4eabe748c8cd8eb2ece13e237369b27312f1","tid":1753571,"uid":3358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"我14歲玩緊彩虹on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac272a4e449821417d6b2ed7bbb083f21155cc2","tid":1753571,"uid":810,"like":1,"dis